  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Activated Recombinant Human Factor VII in Treatment of Bleeding in Patients Following Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel Groups, Placebo-controlled Trial on Efficacy and Safety of Activated Recombinant Factor VII (rFVIIa/NovoSevenÂ®) in the Treatment of Bleeding in Patients Following Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation (HSCT)</official_title>
