  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in the United States of America (USA). The aim of this trial is to
      evaluate the efficacy of activated recombinant human factor VII in treatment of bleeding in
      patients having undergone a hematopoietic stem cell transplantation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
